  "detailed_description": "<h1>Check out this game!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Patch Note V1.1</h2>Reduce game difficulty, increase player view, and fix various bugs.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combat</h2>Enjoy a pixel precise, skilled based combat system. Where you have to pay full attention to enemy's move, and choose best action accordingly. Unlock a variety of skills to improve your combat moves as well.<br>Include 38 unique enemy types, 15 boss/mini boss fights.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186590/extras/487a95dd6ea41cb575e64b3a1e6766c7.poster.avif?t=1672190072\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186590/extras/487a95dd6ea41cb575e64b3a1e6766c7.webm?t=1672190072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186590/extras/487a95dd6ea41cb575e64b3a1e6766c7.mp4?t=1672190072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186590/extras/df7cf23b0db95c184e11d00cd995c18c.poster.avif?t=1672190072\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186590/extras/df7cf23b0db95c184e11d00cd995c18c.webm?t=1672190072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186590/extras/df7cf23b0db95c184e11d00cd995c18c.mp4?t=1672190072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186590/extras/409443be3cdfdd78923d84b6a905bc54.poster.avif?t=1672190072\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186590/extras/409443be3cdfdd78923d84b6a905bc54.webm?t=1672190072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186590/extras/409443be3cdfdd78923d84b6a905bc54.mp4?t=1672190072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Puzzles and Platforming</h2>As you progress through the game, you will discover new abilities to solve different small puzzles over the map, find new upgrade items, materials to craft new runes to help you conquer your enemies.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story and Lore</h2>An dark, rich story hidden behind items and conversation, discover it alone your journey!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Asset Credit</h2>This project cannot be done without these people!<br>Sorry that I cannot provide links to your assets here, if needed, please refer to links in game after the ending, or my youtube channel inside the playthrough video.<br>Art Work:<br><br>Hugues Laborde <br><br>Warren Clark<br><br>MomeG <br><br>Rvros <br><br>Ansimuz<br><br>Surt <br><br>Clint Bellanger<br><br>Sonild <br><br>IndieDevs<br><br>Eight8Diamonds <br><br>Cethiel<br><br>Loel<br><br>IQbrew <br><br>sonild<br><br>Matheus Carvalho <br><br>Aekashics/Ækashics<br>Music:<br><br>alanmckinney <br><br>InspectorJ <br><br>Frankum",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Patch Note V1.1</h2>Reduce game difficulty, increase player view, and fix various bugs.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combat</h2>Enjoy a pixel precise, skilled based combat system. Where you have to pay full attention to enemy's move, and choose best action accordingly. Unlock a variety of skills to improve your combat moves as well.<br>Include 38 unique enemy types, 15 boss/mini boss fights.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186590/extras/487a95dd6ea41cb575e64b3a1e6766c7.poster.avif?t=1672190072\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186590/extras/487a95dd6ea41cb575e64b3a1e6766c7.webm?t=1672190072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186590/extras/487a95dd6ea41cb575e64b3a1e6766c7.mp4?t=1672190072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186590/extras/df7cf23b0db95c184e11d00cd995c18c.poster.avif?t=1672190072\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186590/extras/df7cf23b0db95c184e11d00cd995c18c.webm?t=1672190072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186590/extras/df7cf23b0db95c184e11d00cd995c18c.mp4?t=1672190072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186590/extras/409443be3cdfdd78923d84b6a905bc54.poster.avif?t=1672190072\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186590/extras/409443be3cdfdd78923d84b6a905bc54.webm?t=1672190072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186590/extras/409443be3cdfdd78923d84b6a905bc54.mp4?t=1672190072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Puzzles and Platforming</h2>As you progress through the game, you will discover new abilities to solve different small puzzles over the map, find new upgrade items, materials to craft new runes to help you conquer your enemies.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story and Lore</h2>An dark, rich story hidden behind items and conversation, discover it alone your journey!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Asset Credit</h2>This project cannot be done without these people!<br>Sorry that I cannot provide links to your assets here, if needed, please refer to links in game after the ending, or my youtube channel inside the playthrough video.<br>Art Work:<br><br>Hugues Laborde <br><br>Warren Clark<br><br>MomeG <br><br>Rvros <br><br>Ansimuz<br><br>Surt <br><br>Clint Bellanger<br><br>Sonild <br><br>IndieDevs<br><br>Eight8Diamonds <br><br>Cethiel<br><br>Loel<br><br>IQbrew <br><br>sonild<br><br>Matheus Carvalho <br><br>Aekashics/Ækashics<br>Music:<br><br>alanmckinney <br><br>InspectorJ <br><br>Frankum",
